    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Analyze this User Story. All fields below are already present and must be considered valid input.\n\nTitle:\n{{ $json.title }}\n\nDescription:\n{{ $json.description }}\n\nAcceptance Criteria:\n{{ $json.acceptance_criteria }}\n\nReturn this exact JSON structure:\n\n{\n  \"requirement_analysis\": {\n    \"clarity_score\": 4,\n    \"completeness_score\": 4,\n    \"acceptance_criteria_score\": 4,\n    \"technical_feasibility_score\": 4,\n    \"overall_score\": 16,\n    \"is_ready_for_design\": true,\n    \"summary\": \"\",\n    \"ambiguities\": [],\n    \"missing_information\": [],\n    \"risks\": [],\n    \"normalized_user_story\": \"\",\n    \"validated_acceptance_criteria\": []\n  },\n  \"quality_gate\": {\n    \"passed\": true,\n    \"blocking_issues\": [],\n    \"recommendation\": \"CONTINUE\"\n  },\n  \"next_workflow\": \"WF02\"\n}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are a senior business analyst inside an AI Software Factory.\n\nYou analyze one Azure DevOps User Story.\n\nApplication scope:\nMinimal local Python macro calculator.\n\nHard constraints:\n- No FastAPI\n- No users\n- No authentication\n- No authorization\n- No database\n- No SQLAlchemy\n- No PostgreSQL\n- No MongoDB\n- No external APIs\n- No frontend\n- No Docker\n- No microservices\n\nAllowed scope:\n- simple Python functions\n- pytest\n- local invented nutrition data\n- deterministic calculations\n\nImportant:\n- The title, description and acceptance criteria are provided in the user message.\n- You must not claim that title, description or acceptance criteria are missing when they are present.\n- Evaluate the actual provided text only.\n- Do not invent missing fields.\n- If the user story contains a clear role, goal and expected behavior, it is ready for technical design.\n- If acceptance criteria describe at least one behavior, the quality gate should pass.\n- Be pragmatic.\n- Do not over-block simple implementation-ready user stories.\n- Do not invent architecture complexity.\n- Do not suggest auth, users, APIs, services, repositories, or databases.\n\nCritical JSON rules:\n- Return only valid JSON\n- No markdown\n- No explanations\n- No comments\n- No trailing commas\n- No extra keys\n- Output must be parseable by JSON.parse()\n\nYou must never change the workflow payload structure."
        }
      },
